extendedInfo.description: Are you a traveler ? Or new to the city where you don't know the common places located in the respective city ?  Then "Places Near BY" solves your problems at your finger tip. Just search and select the place you need to locate, and the application does the rest of the work for you and helps you to find local businesses and places with just one click with the help of Google Maps. There are more than 90+ businesses and places supported by the application.The application is very light and easy to use.New In Ver 2.0 :------------------------*All New Attractive User Interface *Minor Bugs FixedNote : Application Uses Google Maps.
